{"tid":26164,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"整左隻迷你腦魔［說好的修正版］","createTime":"2016-12-06T14:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T16:05:35.000Z","uid":611,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cd0e1f1ce8c38583d59287c12abdfe10a16d5e2f","tid":26164,"uid":611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:34:35.000Z","msg":"上個Post說好了的修正版<br />\n本身應承左大家月中會出貨 但呢家出左嚴重意外...<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/06/222857_5ec76259cb8d8638f8270c38d56f433f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F06%2F222857_5ec76259cb8d8638f8270c38d56f433f.jpg&h=f6c9e317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左邊為修正版 右邊為舊版 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌佢老母呀</span>班大陸撚係唔撚會聽人講野架 係唔撚會聽 同佢講多兩句就明明明明 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/06/223101_fa1f0d3b9cafe6c9cddde9ab11fd68d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F06%2F223101_fa1f0d3b9cafe6c9cddde9ab11fd68d7.jpg&h=ccb9e124&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌佢老母整撚左成打 比左錢交D咁既貨黎<br />\n<br />\n但你地放心 我唔會咁無道德畀D咁既野你地既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我已經搵左第二間廠整緊 希望今個星期內會出到個樣辦<br />\n<br />\n嬲嬲地畀晒D異形腦魔隻貓玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <a href=\"https://youtu.be/voHCvT9b5yI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvoHCvT9b5yI&d=gd%2BTSUVBQv6YDf6us6oC4AT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=693fca4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/voHCvT9b5yI</a>"},{"pid":"60b615dc4f41cf4d5a21b47d1ab0d5f3c60c1d90","tid":26164,"uid":611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:35:38.000Z","msg":"次次滿心期待 最後都係失望"},{"pid":"6b90de237f06237f7